data.description: Price to sell and MOVE-IN-READY! This home well cared for and the location is awesome!  Located off Montana Ave and Rich Beam, this home is conveniently located near schools, a movie theater, major shopping and restaurants galore.  Also, located 17 miles or less from the Ft Bliss, TX main gate.  Relax in the low maintenance front and back yards with xericaping, artificial turf, extended concrete slabs around the home, stamped concrete, pergolas, and more amenities.  As you walk in the front door you are welcomed by a large formal living area.  Continue in and find a Texas size family area, dining area and a large bright open kitchen.  Walk out to the gorgeous backyard where you are sure to enjoy and entertain all year round.  In the second level you will find a loft and 3 very spacious bedrooms.  The first floor is all ceramic tile and 2nd level is all wood laminate flooring.  Refrigerate a/c installed 08/2023. Garage door is insulated.  THIS IS A MUST SEE HOME!
